$ Office Object Model: Word - Field

A *field* allows to insert *dynamic text* (such as current page number or date) into a → Microsoft/Office/Word/Object-Model/Document[document].

{ Inserting a page number

  The following → VBA code tries to demonstrate how a page number is inserted into a word document:

  gh|about-MS-Office-object-model|/Word/Field/pageNumber.bas||

  gh|about-MS-Office-object-model|/Word/Field/img/pageNumber.png||

}

sa:
  → Microsoft/Office/Word/Object-Model
